<body>

<div1 type="form">

<pb facs="nei.j4c.3.1" />

<opener>
<salute>Mr. Upton Sinclair:</salute>
</opener>
	<p>You are at liberty to quote from my published work in your anthology of
social protest as per your request of January 10, 1915 to the following extent:
Cry of the People.</p>

<closer>		
<signed>Signed John G. Neihardt</signed>

</closer>
<postscript><p>Born Jan. 8th, 1881</p></postscript>

<fw type="curatorial">1</fw>
</div1>
